name: CornEscape - Don't get harvested.
description: This is a Game where you play a Corn Cob that doesn’t want to get harvested.  In the game, you get chased by the combine harvester, and mice, that want to eat you (because you are a corn cob).  Your objective in the game is to exit the Farm as fast as you can before either the combine harvester or the mice get you.
